Yeo Jun?

29
00:03:12,000 --> 00:03:13,889
Mahasiswa baru yang populer itu?

30
00:03:13,890 --> 00:03:15,609
Anak-anak di kelasku panik.

31
00:03:15,610 --> 00:03:17,549
Pacar Yeo Jun terungkap

32
00:03:17,550 --> 00:03:19,445
di panggung teater terbuka.

33
00:03:20,890 --> 00:03:22,705
Tapi yang benar saja. Kim So-bin?

34
